Here you are, evil hackers !

This script will make you rich. Maybe.

It just sends out twitter update with the hastag #squarespace. Each update act as an entry to the SquareSpace contest (http://www.squarespace.com/iphone). Nothing in the Official Rules forbid us to make a twitter bot. They say that we can apply as many time we want.

Lets win an iPhone !

